scene.message:
Nanjo: Inaba seems to be{nl}
acquainted with those{nl}
police officers.{waitkey}Though he doesn't exactly{nl}
seem glad to see them.{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: You should've seen{nl}
Mark's face. Anyway, aren't{nl}
we going to the hospital?{waitkey}{ret}

Inspector: Oh, if it isn't{nl}
Inaba. You're attending high{nl}
school properly, I hope?{waitkey}You're not causing your{nl}
teachers any trouble?{waitkey}{ret}

Inspector: Still, I'm the one{nl}
who hauled you in once. So{nl}
there's the matter of{nl}
responsibility...{waitkey}{ret}

Policewoman: Inspector,{nl}
that's too harsh. Inaba's{nl}
a good kid, aren't you?{waitkey}{ret}

Policewoman: You're a friend{nl}
of Inaba's, aren't you? I'm{nl}
fond of him. Don't you think{nl}
he's a good kid?{waitkey}{ret}
